一直以来，陈时中面对所有对于疫苗的质疑，比如接种疫苗后出现不良反应、死亡等情况时的统一说法。前文所述昨天台湾当局发布的《COVID-19 疫苗接种后不良事件通报》中，官方也一直在强调，「（这份文件）本身不能解释或用于得出疫苗相关问题之存在与否、严重程度、频率或发生率的结论。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-623b2df0dfa9a9bad0749195b94a25b2_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/491156945"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqqjC363Z6dMvEAMaCDcxNDI3NDM5ILTr/ooGMGg46QdAK3IJNDkxMTU2OTQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1633752231.7289991", "card_id": "Q_489938038", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 10 月新番动画《古见同学有交流障碍症》第一集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7e0b4ef6abdb075296dd55f74974e27d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489938038"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIqqjC363Z6dMvEAMaCDcxMTU2NDU0IK2P1YoGMAA4IEAscgk0ODk5MzgwMzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1633752231.7294853", "card_id": "Q_490799816", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 Jennie 的巴黎时装周造型？你觉得好看吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-0eae1809e4230b9559cf7c36edf00738_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/490799816"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqqjC363Z6dMvEAMaCDcxMzQ3OTg3IOP28YoGMAQ4gAFALXIJNDkwNzk5ODE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1633752231.7299988", "card_id": "Q_491074540", "feed_s